author: Reuters Editorial
title: Russian senator says Moscow will expel dozens of U.S. diplomats
text:
MOSCOW (Reuters) - Moscow will expel at least 60 staff from U.S. diplomatic missions in Russia in response to Washingtonâ€™s decision to expel Russian diplomats, RIA news agency Quote: d a member of the upper house of the Russian parliament as saying.
The agency did not say on what the parliamentarian, Vladimir Dzhabarov, deputy chairman of the international affairs committee in the upper house, based his assertion. Government officials have yet to comment.
(Corrects attribution in first paragraph to show RIA news agency was the source of the information.)
